---
title: Harissa-Spiced Roast Lamb with Roast Potatoes, Cheesy Cauli, Chantenay Carrots and Gravy
description: We love a good Lamb with Potatoes, Cheesy Cauli & Gravy and this deliciously simple, chef-curated recipe doesn't disappoint. Time to bust out the pots and pans!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/harissa-spiced-roast-lamb-2c15fbe5-b1517ffc.jpg
